&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">●</span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">ChatGPT：每日使用；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">●</span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Gemini：</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">处理技术类任务</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">●</span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Grok：用于创意类内容；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">●</span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Perplexity：用于快速</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">检索、</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">调研。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">除了 xAI 的 Grok，其余 AI 模型背后的公司均与英伟达有合作，本月又与 Anthropic 建立了战略合作伙伴关系，</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\" data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">估计 Claude 也即将加入黄仁勋的个人 AI 工具链。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100252190\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11428571428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"700\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c02173a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FPn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06Q0QtgZAx8xsoTReptvArfwbn9MvHGVfV98Qkl5PMRS6MCt2ljwLJwoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">黄仁勋</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">坚信：</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">AI 不会抢走人类工作</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">事实上，在这次内部讲话曝光之外，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">黄仁勋过去几个月也在各种公开场合不断输出一个概念：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">“抢走你工作的不是 AI，而是比你更会用 AI 的人。”</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;\" data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在他看来，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">员工要把能交给模型的部分全部自动化，剩下的才是“需要人类判断、协调以及新出现任务”的地方。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">后来在&nbsp;</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">CNN 的采访中，黄仁勋也进一步解释道：“我可以确定，每个人的工作都会被 AI 改变。但改变的是工作内</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">容，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不是岗位本身。只要世界不停止创新，生产力提升不会带来失业。</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">”</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">——</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">正</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">是他</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">努力向公众、投资者，甚至自家员工灌输的反焦虑</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">观点</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">然而，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如今</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">英伟达面临的现实是：</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">就算</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">技术上&nbsp;</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">AI&nbsp;</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">已无所不能，但在人这一层，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">其</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">惰性</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">和</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">使用习惯是最慢也最难改的。</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如上文所说</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">英伟达</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">大约有 36000 名员工，要让这</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">些</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">人</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在每个工作流程中都养成“先问&nbsp;</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">AI”的肌肉记忆，</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">显然</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不是</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">光</span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">靠一场全员会就能解决的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;margin-right:8px;\"><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">参考链接</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">：</span></span></span><span data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/nvidia-ceo-employees-use-ai-every-task-possible-2025-11\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.businessinsider.com/nvidia-ceo-employees-use-ai-every-task-possible-2025-11</a></span></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "英伟达 CEO 黄仁勋强调公司必须全面拥抱 AI 自动化所有任务，认为 AI 是提升效率而非威胁，并承诺员工永远有事可做。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "英伟达 CEO 黄仁勋强调公司必须全面拥抱 AI 自动化所有任务，认为 AI 是提升效率而非威胁，并承诺员工永远有事可做。",
  "summary": "文章报道了英伟达 CEO 黄仁勋在内部会议上对要求员工少用 AI 的管理者发飙，强调公司必须将所有可自动化任务交由 AI 完成，并指出即使 AI 暂时做得不好也要持续使用并改进。他同时向员工保证，AI 是提升竞争力的工具而非威胁，公司仍在大量招聘以满足数据中心需求。文章还披露了英伟达内部工程师使用 AI 编码助手 Cursor 的现状，以及黄仁勋本人作为多款 AI 工具深度用户的事实。黄仁勋坚信 AI 不会抢走人类工作，而是改变工作内容，只要世界不停止创新，生产力提升不会带来失业，但文章也指出改变员工使用习惯是最大的挑战。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "黄仁勋强力推动 AI 在英伟达内部的全面自动化应用。",
      "explanation": "他认为所有能被 AI 自动化的任务都必须自动化，即使 AI 暂时不完善也要持续使用并改进，以提高效率和竞争力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 是员工保持竞争力的基础能力，而非工作威胁。",
      "explanation": "黄仁勋强调 AI 不会抢走人类工作，而是改变工作内容，员工应积极利用 AI 提升自身价值，英伟达也因此持续扩张招聘。"
    },
    {
      "point": "英伟达内部已开始广泛采用 AI 工具，CEO 本人更是深度用户。",
      "explanation": "工程师已使用 AI 编码助手 Cursor，黄仁勋本人也日常使用 ChatGPT、Gemini 等多种 AI 工具，身体力行推动 AI 化。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
